```

## Examples

See the `examples/` directory for complete working examples:

- **[Python FastAPI](https://github.com/LLMdotInfo/ldf/blob/main/examples/python-fastapi/)** - User authentication with JWT, MFA
- **[Python Flask](https://github.com/LLMdotInfo/ldf/blob/main/examples/python-flask/)** - Blog API with SQLAlchemy, Blueprints
- **[Python Django](https://github.com/LLMdotInfo/ldf/blob/main/examples/python-django/)** - E-commerce API with DRF, multi-tenancy
- **[TypeScript Node](https://github.com/LLMdotInfo/ldf/blob/main/examples/typescript-node/)** - REST API with Prisma, Zod validation
- **[Go Service](https://github.com/LLMdotInfo/ldf/blob/main/examples/go-service/)** - Data pipeline with Chi router

### Recommended Additional Examples

See [examples/RECOMMENDATIONS.md](https://github.com/LLMdotInfo/ldf/blob/main/examples/RECOMMENDATIONS.md) for proposals on 5 additional framework examples (Rust, Java, Ruby, C#, PHP) to expand the collection to 10 total templates.

Each example includes:
- `.ldf/` configuration
- Complete spec (requirements â†’ design â†’ tasks)
- `AGENT.md` project instructions

